import React from 'react'
import ReactDom from 'react-dom'
import Card from './Card'
ReactDom.render(
  <>
    <Card imgsrc="https://images-na.ssl-images-amazon.com/images/I/51Y-4b1Ux0L._SY450_.jpg" title="A Netflix original series" fname="Dark" olink="https://www.netflix.com/in/title/80100172" />
    <Card imgsrc="https://www.maacindia.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/n-panchayat.jpg" title="Best Comedy Series" fname="Panchyat" olink="https://www.primevideo.com/detail/0KEP4A6DWRKFYQFTSU5RXHEAN2/%7Cm_c_c452441516049" />
    <Card imgsrc="data:image/jpeg;base64," title="Best Web series" fname="The Family Man" olink="https://www.amazon.com/The-Family-Man-Season-1/dp/B086HVMNT2" />
    <Card />
  </>, document.getElementById('root')
)
